418
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] i onda u toj teoriji igara imamo jedan model igre,

419
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] to je zatvorenikova dilema.

420
