761
01:03:13,760 --> 01:03:19,380
[SPEAKER_09] Dakle, to postaje po meni, već onako, neće se svatko moći za jedno pet godina

762
01:03:19,380 --> 01:03:22,739
[SPEAKER_09] osmijehnuti na ideje, evo, ove o kojima sad pričamo.

763
01:03:22,739 --> 01:03:27,900
[SPEAKER_09] Jer imam osjećaj da će se ljudi ipak obrazovat da to ide u pozitivnu smjeru.

764
01:03:27,900 --> 01:03:32,599
[SPEAKER_09] Osobno i jesam pozitivna. Znači, koliko god da ovo je loše,

765
01:03:32,599 --> 01:03:38,639
[SPEAKER_09] imam ošte da nekako se tu na zapadu stvara ta slika da više nije nekom tako svejedno

766
01:03:38,639 --> 01:03:40,880
[SPEAKER_09] bacit papir nasred sesterega, nije briga.

767
01:03:41,119 --> 01:03:43,280
[SPEAKER_09] Jer već ima neki i onaj unutarnji sram.

768
01:03:43,280 --> 01:03:48,940
[SPEAKER_09] Tako da, eto, nadam se da smo na pravom mjestu sada

769
01:03:48,940 --> 01:03:52,719
[SPEAKER_09] da možemo i dalje razvijati ideje koje će, eto, nadam se, proizvati.

770
01:03:52,719 --> 01:03:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je bilo jako zanimljivo promatrati kako pojedini novinari

771
01:03:59,679 --> 01:04:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] i pojedini medijima komentiraju ovo što se događalo.

772
01:04:02,719 --> 01:04:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja se opet vraćam sa Superligom jer je baš i stvarno zanimljivo.

773
01:04:09,360 --> 01:04:14,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta, zašto, kao da smo svi mi najedni romantičari.

774
01:04:14,179 --> 01:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo najedni romantičari koji nas treba, pa u kojem svijetu mi živimo.

775
01:04:19,000 --> 01:04:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tako je normalno da oni traže veću dobiti.

776
01:04:21,679 --> 01:04:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kao da je to nešto čudno.

777
01:04:23,159 --> 01:04:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta, pa da ne traži i onaj koji proizvodi uljanu repicu veću dobiti, veću zaradu.

778
01:04:28,800 --> 01:04:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] A, zapravo, što je na stvari, što je po sredi?

779
01:04:31,960 --> 01:04:39,280
[SPEAKER_01] Po sredi je totalni despotizam ekonomije i ekonomskih vrijednosti kao ultimativnih i konačnih.

780
01:04:39,280 --> 01:04:41,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gdje ekonomija daje prvu i zadnju riječ.

781
01:04:41,760 --> 01:04:44,219
[SPEAKER_01] I ono što je isplativo, to je okej.

782
01:04:44,219 --> 01:04:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što nije isplativo, nije u redu i nikakve druge vrijednosti ne postoje.

783
01:04:47,619 --> 01:04:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] A mi znamo da to nije tako.

784
01:04:49,739 --> 01:04:53,760
[SPEAKER_01] Mi znamo da nije tako i da mi, svatko od nas, ima neke svoje vrijednosti.

785
01:04:53,760 --> 01:04:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ima neki sustav vrijednosti uz koje pristaje i uz koje ne pristaje.

786
01:04:58,920 --> 01:05:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se možemo i ne poduzaramo u tom sustavu vrijednosti.

787
01:05:02,980 --> 01:05:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala.

788
01:05:03,780 --> 01:05:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nisu nam ekonomski pojmovi alfa i omega.

789
01:05:09,199 --> 01:05:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se postavi kao da je konačni odgovor na sva pitanja da je račun dobiti gubitka.

790
01:05:16,639 --> 01:05:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to suma, jestli u plusu ili minusu?

791
01:05:19,380 --> 01:05:22,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, što više u plusu, to je kao bolje za društvo.

792
01:05:22,320 --> 01:05:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] A znamo, evo i Dijana kaže, i činjenica je, ono što je bolje za pojedinca,

793
01:05:27,199 --> 01:05:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] ne mora biti bolje za društvo.

794
01:05:28,280 --> 01:05:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, brojne firme su se obogatili na sjeći tih šuma.

795
01:05:31,599 --> 01:05:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] Brojni pojedinci su se obogatili na sjeći tih šuma.

796
01:05:34,320 --> 01:05:35,760
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje, i tako dalje.

797
01:05:35,760 --> 01:05:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to ne znači da je to dobro za društvo.

798
01:05:37,400 --> 01:05:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] Nije dobro za društvo u cijeliniji.

799
01:05:40,019 --> 01:05:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se vraćamo na ovo predavanje opet prostora Brunija.

800
01:05:42,619 --> 01:05:46,219
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, što je to, na koji način se mi udružujemo u društvo,

801
01:05:46,219 --> 01:05:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] da bi to društvo prosperirao i očuvalo opiče dobro,

802
01:05:49,699 --> 01:05:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] nasozajedničko dobro za buduće generacije.

803
01:05:52,099 --> 01:05:54,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kako mi definiramo to,

804
01:05:54,480 --> 01:05:59,820
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način mi gradimo to društvo.

805
01:05:59,820 --> 01:06:01,659
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to super zanimljivo.

806
01:06:01,659 --> 01:06:04,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nadam da i vama baremo koliko je toliko.

807
01:06:08,440 --> 01:06:11,199
[SPEAKER_09] Jako je zanimljiva tema.

808
01:06:11,199 --> 01:06:15,739
[SPEAKER_09] Tako da, slobodno, neka se ljudi uključe u raspravu.

809
01:06:15,739 --> 01:06:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja ću samo na trenutak još objaviti,

810
01:06:19,519 --> 01:06:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] onda pokazati rezultate,

811
01:06:21,199 --> 01:06:24,239
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga što smo glasovali.

812
01:06:24,239 --> 01:06:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] Većina ljudi je bila mislila da će te zvršiti na ekonomiji,

813
01:06:29,280 --> 01:06:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] nije nego na filozofiji.

814
01:06:34,440 --> 01:06:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] Većina ljudi je odgovorila ipak 60% da većina ljudi,

815
01:06:40,820 --> 01:06:42,219
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno većina studijenika,

816
01:06:42,219 --> 01:06:44,619
[SPEAKER_01] da većina građana ima osjećaj,

817
01:06:44,619 --> 01:06:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] ima osjećaj za prirod.

818
01:06:45,719 --> 01:06:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nas to očito, to je ta tragedija

819
01:06:49,960 --> 01:06:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] i to je vrlo čest pojem,

820
01:06:51,000 --> 01:06:52,320
[SPEAKER_01] taj tragedija zajedničku dobra,

821
01:06:52,320 --> 01:06:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] tražiti ovdje komans,

822
01:06:53,119 --> 01:06:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] koja se često koristi i koja je,

823
01:06:54,679 --> 01:06:59,719
[SPEAKER_01] koja je, možda sad aktualnija nego ikada.

824
01:06:59,719 --> 01:07:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nema pitanja, ja bih se zahvalio

825
01:07:02,639 --> 01:07:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] i nećemo sadržavati više ljude,

826
01:07:04,440 --> 01:07:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] hvala vam što ste popratili,

827
01:07:06,159 --> 01:07:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] hvala vam što ste sudjelovali.

828
01:07:07,579 --> 01:07:11,179
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da ćete pogledati

829
01:07:11,179 --> 01:07:12,980
[SPEAKER_01] originalno predavanje profesora Brunija,

830
01:07:12,980 --> 01:07:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] da će vam sad biti puno razumljivije.

831
01:07:16,260 --> 01:07:17,940
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da će biti razumljivije

832
01:07:17,940 --> 01:07:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] i jednostavnije za shvatiti,

833
01:07:19,099 --> 01:07:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] što je pod navodicima pjesnih tio reći.

834
01:07:22,099 --> 01:07:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] Prof. domagoj, mogu ja samo još jedno pitanje,

835
01:07:24,900 --> 01:07:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] ako ima vremena piše do sedam,

836
01:07:26,679 --> 01:07:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako nije ovaj...

837
01:07:27,980 --> 01:07:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, ja...

838
01:07:28,840 --> 01:07:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se neće ljudi na ljudstvu ovdje, ovaj...

839
01:07:31,960 --> 01:07:33,460
[SPEAKER_05] Ne, da paća, izvolite.

840
01:07:33,900 --> 01:07:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, leo, dižem roku već tri puta,

841
01:07:36,199 --> 01:07:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa da ispadja, da s tomo pozdravljam.

842
01:07:38,260 --> 01:07:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, evo, od srca bih vam se prvo zahvalio

843
01:07:41,780 --> 01:07:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] što ste me ovdje pozvali,

844
01:07:43,320 --> 01:07:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] jer kao vaš kolega profesora

845
01:07:46,320 --> 01:07:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] i diplomira sam i magistrirao

846
01:07:47,739 --> 01:07:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] na Ekonomskom fakultetu u Osijeku.

847
01:07:49,639 --> 01:07:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Trenutno sam zbog nekih možda

848
01:07:52,599 --> 01:07:53,760
[SPEAKER_00] i političkih razloga

849
01:07:53,760 --> 01:07:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] dosta dugo nezaposlen

850
01:07:55,920 --> 01:07:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] već sam mislio da sam skroz izašao iz ekonomije

851
01:07:59,099 --> 01:08:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] i sad dobijem poziv na ovako nešto,

852
01:08:01,380 --> 01:08:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam baš sretan da mogu sudjelovati

853
01:08:03,199 --> 01:08:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] na nekom predavanju

854
01:08:04,179 --> 01:08:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] i nešto čut i novo naučiti.

855
01:08:06,559 --> 01:08:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mene, profesore, zanima

856
01:08:08,400 --> 01:08:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] s ova pitanja koja ste vi naveli

857
01:08:10,739 --> 01:08:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] i kolege i kolegice

858
01:08:12,179 --> 01:08:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] su stvarno složena

859
01:08:13,820 --> 01:08:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da ću puno o tome naučiti

860
01:08:16,159 --> 01:08:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] kroz ljudiče predavanje

861
01:08:17,340 --> 01:08:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] i kroz raspravo i praćenje.

862
01:08:19,000 --> 01:08:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mene zanima da li se nešto može konkretizirati

863
01:08:22,619 --> 01:08:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] na mikrooperativnoj razini

864
01:08:24,659 --> 01:08:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] što ste vi spomenuli tržište

865
01:08:26,859 --> 01:08:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] i što je gospođo, mislim, Kristina

866
01:08:28,739 --> 01:08:30,180
[SPEAKER_00] rekla novi modeli.

867
01:08:30,180 --> 01:08:33,439
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ako postoji pranjina ekonomija,

868
01:08:33,439 --> 01:08:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] da li postoji mogućnost

869
01:08:35,300 --> 01:08:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] ako su to, ne znam,

870
01:08:36,500 --> 01:08:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] stotine timova u različitim zemljama

871
01:08:39,380 --> 01:08:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] da postoji jedna digitalna platforma

872
01:08:42,380 --> 01:08:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] za ekonomiju

873
01:08:44,260 --> 01:08:46,359
[SPEAKER_00] i recimo da se razmišlja

874
01:08:46,359 --> 01:08:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] sad malo lupam,

875
01:08:48,180 --> 01:08:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali recimo,

876
01:08:49,340 --> 01:08:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] a nek su dobra sva zajednička,

877
01:08:52,279 --> 01:08:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, da neko na toj digitalnoj platformi

878
01:08:55,300 --> 01:08:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] pranjine ekonomije

879
01:08:56,399 --> 01:08:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] postavi recimo

880
01:08:58,279 --> 01:08:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] zbirku pjesama,

881
01:08:59,619 --> 01:09:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] neko postavi knjigu,

882
01:09:00,779 --> 01:09:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] neko postavi spot,

883
01:09:01,840 --> 01:09:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] neko postavi kratak film,

884
01:09:03,260 --> 01:09:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] neko postavi neko digitalno dobro,

885
01:09:05,579 --> 01:09:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] neko može postaviti toglaz

886
01:09:07,199 --> 01:09:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] za stvarno dobro

887
01:09:08,279 --> 01:09:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] recimo ako proizvodi kruške.

888
01:09:11,159 --> 01:09:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

889
01:09:12,880 --> 01:09:14,560
[SPEAKER_00] u konkretnom smislu,

890
01:09:14,560 --> 01:09:15,479
[SPEAKER_00] kroz tržište,

891
01:09:15,800 --> 01:09:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali sa jasno mjerljivim sustavom

892
01:09:18,420 --> 01:09:19,899
[SPEAKER_00] vrijednosti i ciljeva

893
01:09:19,899 --> 01:09:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] kako ostvariti,

894
01:09:20,859 --> 01:09:21,899
[SPEAKER_00] koliki dio recimo

895
01:09:21,899 --> 01:09:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] tog prodanog dobra

896
01:09:22,800 --> 01:09:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] na tržištu

897
01:09:23,819 --> 01:09:24,520
[SPEAKER_00] može ići

898
01:09:24,520 --> 01:09:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] za ciljeve franjine ekonomije,

899
01:09:26,420 --> 01:09:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] za siromašne,

900
01:09:27,340 --> 01:09:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] za isključene,

901
01:09:28,359 --> 01:09:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] za neke aktivnosti

902
01:09:30,819 --> 01:09:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] humanitarne,

903
01:09:33,079 --> 01:09:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] koliko može ići

904
01:09:34,479 --> 01:09:36,020
[SPEAKER_00] u dalje poduzetništvo.

905
01:09:36,020 --> 01:09:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] I još jedna stvar me zanima,

906
01:09:37,859 --> 01:09:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] da li postoji mogućnost,

907
01:09:39,920 --> 01:09:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] puno se sad u zadnji vrijeme

908
01:09:41,380 --> 01:09:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] govore o digitalnim valutama.

909
01:09:43,180 --> 01:09:44,439
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

910
01:09:44,439 --> 01:09:45,520
[SPEAKER_00] i svi govore o nekakvom

911
01:09:45,520 --> 01:09:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] rodarenju

912
01:09:46,140 --> 01:09:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] i matematičkim izračunima valuta.

913
01:09:48,359 --> 01:09:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mene sad zanima

914
01:09:49,960 --> 01:09:51,060
[SPEAKER_00] da li je moguće

915
01:09:51,060 --> 01:09:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] napraviti digitalnu valutu

916
01:09:52,539 --> 01:09:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] kao primjer svijetu

917
01:09:53,659 --> 01:09:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] temeljenu

918
01:09:54,680 --> 01:09:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] na nekim duhovnim

919
01:09:56,239 --> 01:09:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] etičkim vrijednostima.

920
01:09:57,539 --> 01:09:58,479
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

921
01:09:58,479 --> 01:10:01,020
[SPEAKER_00] ako je matematička formula

922
01:10:01,020 --> 01:10:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] bit za izračun bitcoina

923
01:10:04,060 --> 01:10:05,220
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne znam ja što,

924
01:10:05,220 --> 01:10:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] da li snaga može biti

925
01:10:07,659 --> 01:10:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

926
01:10:08,119 --> 01:10:10,140
[SPEAKER_00] u pozadina

927
01:10:10,140 --> 01:10:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] virtualnog novca

928
01:10:11,619 --> 01:10:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] temeljenog

929
01:10:12,180 --> 01:10:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] na recimo

930
01:10:12,939 --> 01:10:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] nekoj kršćanskoj valuti

931
01:10:14,180 --> 01:10:15,020
[SPEAKER_00] recimo

932
01:10:15,020 --> 01:10:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] neka

933
01:10:15,399 --> 01:10:17,020
[SPEAKER_00] neka pjesma

934
01:10:17,020 --> 01:10:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] ili poezija

935
01:10:17,760 --> 01:10:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto tako.

936
01:10:18,779 --> 01:10:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

937
01:10:19,819 --> 01:10:21,300
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljati o konceptima

938
01:10:21,300 --> 01:10:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] drugačijim novca

939
01:10:22,619 --> 01:10:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] i u konceptima

940
01:10:24,960 --> 01:10:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] drugačijim razmjene.

941
01:10:26,079 --> 01:10:27,659
[SPEAKER_00] Možda bi se na toj platformi

942
01:10:27,659 --> 01:10:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] moglo plaćati

943
01:10:28,800 --> 01:10:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] nekom novom valutom,

944
01:10:30,000 --> 01:10:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] franjinom valutom

945
01:10:31,119 --> 01:10:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] između sudionika.

946
01:10:32,140 --> 01:10:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mora biti

947
01:10:33,140 --> 01:10:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] stvarni novac

948
01:10:33,819 --> 01:10:34,899
[SPEAKER_00] kao primjer svijetu,

949
01:10:34,899 --> 01:10:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] neke bolje ekonomije.

950
01:10:36,319 --> 01:10:37,899
[SPEAKER_00] Možda malo lupa,

951
01:10:37,899 --> 01:10:39,439
[SPEAKER_00] malo mislim da se na neki način

952
01:10:39,439 --> 01:10:41,479
[SPEAKER_00] među svojim kolegicama

953
01:10:41,479 --> 01:10:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] i kolegama,

954
01:10:42,159 --> 01:10:43,479
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi oprostite.

955
01:10:43,479 --> 01:10:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako možete kratko reći?

956
01:10:44,920 --> 01:10:46,939
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

957
01:10:46,939 --> 01:10:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo kratko.

958
01:10:48,840 --> 01:10:49,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

959
01:10:49,180 --> 01:10:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] što se tiče,

960
01:10:50,359 --> 01:10:52,640
[SPEAKER_01] prepostajem da u tom pravcu

961
01:10:52,640 --> 01:10:53,399
[SPEAKER_01] ide pitanje

962
01:10:53,399 --> 01:10:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] konkretizacije,

963
01:10:54,880 --> 01:10:56,600
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno na neki način

964
01:10:56,600 --> 01:10:58,100
[SPEAKER_01] primjene ovih

965
01:10:58,100 --> 01:10:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] principa u praksi

966
01:10:59,720 --> 01:11:00,979
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način,

967
01:11:00,979 --> 01:11:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] ako sam dobro razumio,

968
01:11:02,300 --> 01:11:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] da li postoji platforma

969
01:11:04,739 --> 01:11:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] na koji ćemo mi jedni druga

970
01:11:06,140 --> 01:11:06,720
[SPEAKER_01] prepoznati.

971
01:11:06,720 --> 01:11:09,140
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da postoji,

972
01:11:09,140 --> 01:11:10,359
[SPEAKER_01] kao da bismo razvili

973
01:11:10,359 --> 01:11:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvu etiketu,

974
01:11:11,500 --> 01:11:12,560
[SPEAKER_01] nekakav,

975
01:11:12,560 --> 01:11:13,180
[SPEAKER_01] rekli bismo,

976
01:11:13,180 --> 01:11:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] label,

977
01:11:13,659 --> 01:11:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi onda stavili

978
01:11:14,680 --> 01:11:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] na svoj proizvod

979
01:11:15,460 --> 01:11:16,220
[SPEAKER_01] i na svoju uslugu,

980
01:11:16,220 --> 01:11:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa bi onda mi jedni druga

981
01:11:17,300 --> 01:11:18,600
[SPEAKER_01] namirisali i onda bi shvatili

982
01:11:18,600 --> 01:11:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] aha,

983
01:11:18,859 --> 01:11:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] iza ovoga stoje neke vrijednosti,

984
01:11:20,960 --> 01:11:22,939
[SPEAKER_01] a iza onoga ne stoje neke vrijednosti.

985
01:11:24,539 --> 01:11:28,220
[SPEAKER_01] Za sada tako nešto ne postoji,

986
01:11:28,220 --> 01:11:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer,

987
01:11:29,340 --> 01:11:32,640
[SPEAKER_01] zašto?

988
01:11:32,640 --> 01:11:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osobno,

989
01:11:34,819 --> 01:11:37,060
[SPEAKER_01] recimo ako pitate mene konkretno,

990
01:11:37,060 --> 01:11:38,880
[SPEAKER_01] ja osobno sam malo podvojnog mišljenja

991
01:11:38,880 --> 01:11:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] oko toga.

992
01:11:39,260 --> 01:11:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] S jedne strane,

993
01:11:39,760 --> 01:11:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] bilo bi dobro da tako nešto postoji,

994
01:11:41,359 --> 01:11:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] da možemo prepoznati jedni i druge

995
01:11:42,960 --> 01:11:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoj šumi proizvoda i usluga,

996
01:11:45,300 --> 01:11:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] a s druge strane,

997
01:11:46,539 --> 01:11:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] je to bolo stiznak teren,

998
01:11:47,699 --> 01:11:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer onda zapravo na neki način

999
01:11:49,420 --> 01:11:50,779
[SPEAKER_01] se označujemo jedni i druge,

1000
01:11:50,779 --> 01:11:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] a neko će ostati,

1001
01:11:52,880 --> 01:11:54,779
[SPEAKER_01] neko će definitivno ostati neoznačen,

1002
01:11:54,779 --> 01:11:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] a treba biti označen,

1003
01:11:56,079 --> 01:11:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] a neko će imati taj,

1004
01:11:57,520 --> 01:11:59,279
[SPEAKER_01] steći će tu oznaku,

1005
01:11:59,279 --> 01:12:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] a ne bi je trebao imati.

1006
01:12:00,319 --> 01:12:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam,

1007
01:12:01,779 --> 01:12:03,819
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću otvoriti recimo nekakvu firmu

1008
01:12:03,819 --> 01:12:05,779
[SPEAKER_01] i dobit ću tu oznaku

1009
01:12:05,779 --> 01:12:07,640
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način ću diskreditirati,

1010
01:12:07,640 --> 01:12:10,279
[SPEAKER_01] recimo napravim nešto pogrešno,

1011
01:12:10,279 --> 01:12:11,939
[SPEAKER_01] ne isplaćujem svoje radnike,

1012
01:12:11,939 --> 01:12:13,939
[SPEAKER_01] prevarim svoje radnike,

1013
01:12:13,939 --> 01:12:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] prevarim svoje dobavljače

1014
01:12:15,260 --> 01:12:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] i pobjegnem sa novcem na Maldive,

1015
01:12:18,079 --> 01:12:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] a moj proizvod ima tu oznaku.

1016
01:12:21,420 --> 01:12:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način ću diskreditirati,

1017
01:12:23,420 --> 01:12:24,520
[SPEAKER_01] diskreditirati,

1018
01:12:24,520 --> 01:12:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] samo trenutno.

1019
01:12:25,840 --> 01:12:32,739
[SPEAKER_05] To se dešava u Njemačkoj.

1020
01:12:33,260 --> 01:12:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam u obitelji,

1021
01:12:34,579 --> 01:12:38,439
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi kod kuće sam,

1022
01:12:38,439 --> 01:12:42,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa obiteljska intervencija.

1023
01:12:42,279 --> 01:12:47,359
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, diskreditirati će tu etiketu

1024
01:12:47,359 --> 01:12:48,779
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ćemo svi biti tu problemu

1025
01:12:48,779 --> 01:12:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] zato što je domagli sajter

1026
01:12:50,420 --> 01:12:52,560
[SPEAKER_01] pokrao svoje dobavljače

1027
01:12:52,560 --> 01:12:53,520
[SPEAKER_01] i pobjegao na Maldive,

1028
01:12:53,520 --> 01:12:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] a imao je tu etiketu.

1029
01:12:55,420 --> 01:12:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] I to je jedan problem.

1030
01:12:57,520 --> 01:13:00,439
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi problem je komodifikacije.

1031
01:13:00,439 --> 01:13:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sve pretpadamo u robu.

1032
01:13:01,420 --> 01:13:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz proces komodifikacije

1033
01:13:04,720 --> 01:13:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] sve postaje roba.

1034
01:13:06,199 --> 01:13:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i naše vrijednosti postaju roba.

1035
01:13:08,619 --> 01:13:10,020
[SPEAKER_01] A mi, ja osobno,

1036
01:13:10,020 --> 01:13:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] nisam baš

1037
01:13:10,920 --> 01:13:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] zato da vrijednosti postanu

1038
01:13:15,699 --> 01:13:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] još jedna u nizu roba

1039
01:13:17,180 --> 01:13:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] koja se kupuje i prodaje.

1040
01:13:18,819 --> 01:13:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] vrijednosti trebaju biti utkane

1041
01:13:20,119 --> 01:13:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] u društvo na nekakav

1042
01:13:22,159 --> 01:13:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] subtilniji i drugačiji način,

1043
01:13:25,180 --> 01:13:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] a ne kroz ozniku ili kroz digitalnu platbu.

1044
01:13:28,079 --> 01:13:29,279
[SPEAKER_01] I samo ovo,

1045
01:13:29,279 --> 01:13:30,859
[SPEAKER_01] znači, što tiče digitalna valuta,

1046
01:13:30,859 --> 01:13:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno novca,

1047
01:13:31,699 --> 01:13:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] novac je onoliko novac

1048
01:13:34,420 --> 01:13:36,220
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ga ljudi prihvaćaju kao novac.

1049
01:13:36,220 --> 01:13:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ponovit ću.

1050
01:13:37,880 --> 01:13:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, novac je onoliko novac

1051
01:13:39,539 --> 01:13:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ga ljudi prihvaćaju kao novac.

1052
01:13:41,000 --> 01:13:42,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ćemo svi prihvaćati

1053
01:13:42,439 --> 01:13:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] da je kemijska novac,

1054
01:13:46,300 --> 01:13:48,060
[SPEAKER_01] onda će kemijska postati novac.

1055
01:13:48,439 --> 01:13:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ako u zatvorima zatvarnici prihvaćaju

1056
01:13:51,340 --> 01:13:52,319
[SPEAKER_01] da su cigarete novac

1057
01:13:52,319 --> 01:13:53,920
[SPEAKER_01] i cigarete funkcioniraju kao novac.

1058
01:13:53,920 --> 01:13:55,720
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, nijedan novac se ne može

1059
01:13:55,720 --> 01:13:56,859
[SPEAKER_01] nametnuti kao novac

1060
01:13:56,859 --> 01:13:57,720
[SPEAKER_01] ako ga ljudi ne prihvate.

1061
01:13:57,720 --> 01:13:59,819
[SPEAKER_01] Bitcoin su mnogi ljudi prihvatili,

1062
01:13:59,819 --> 01:14:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] pa može funkcionirati kao novac.

1063
01:14:01,180 --> 01:14:02,319
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ljudi ga opet,

1064
01:14:02,319 --> 01:14:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo većina svijeskostalništoga

1065
01:14:04,720 --> 01:14:06,180
[SPEAKER_01] i dalje ne prihvaće kao novac

1066
01:14:06,180 --> 01:14:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] i zato ne možete kupiti kifra sa bitcoinovom.

1067
01:14:08,340 --> 01:14:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] I ako ćemo uvesti nekakav novac

1068
01:14:11,460 --> 01:14:14,060
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima duhovne vrijednosti,

1069
01:14:14,119 --> 01:14:16,220
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno koji ima nekako drugačiju teme,

1070
01:14:16,220 --> 01:14:17,140
[SPEAKER_01] drugačiju podlogu,

1071
01:14:17,140 --> 01:14:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] to opet ne može se nikome nametnuti

1072
01:14:19,920 --> 01:14:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] i opet će biti obisno o tome

1073
01:14:21,260 --> 01:14:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] koliko će ga ljudi prihvaćati ili ne.

1074
01:14:25,119 --> 01:14:26,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pokušao sam skratiti maksimalno.

1075
01:14:26,779 --> 01:14:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ima ovdje i drugih sudjelnika

1076
01:14:28,460 --> 01:14:29,479
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi mogli odgovoriti,

1077
01:14:29,479 --> 01:14:30,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa slobodno odgovorite.

1078
01:14:30,460 --> 01:14:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] Profesora, hvala.

1079
01:14:33,260 --> 01:14:38,060
[SPEAKER_08] Dok neko može, želi postaviti pitanje,

1080
01:14:38,060 --> 01:14:40,600
[SPEAKER_08] ja bi se osvrnula na jednu riječ

1081
01:14:40,600 --> 01:14:41,739
[SPEAKER_08] koja me je posebno zazvolila

1082
01:14:41,739 --> 01:14:44,279
[SPEAKER_08] kod profesora kad je rekao

1083
01:14:44,279 --> 01:14:46,460
[SPEAKER_08] da trebamo se prestati ponašati

1084
01:14:46,460 --> 01:14:47,460
[SPEAKER_08] ko vlasnici.

1085
01:14:47,460 --> 01:14:49,520
[SPEAKER_08] Pa nekako je to me nasocijiralo

1086
01:14:49,520 --> 01:14:51,539
[SPEAKER_08] na neko rješenje

1087
01:14:51,539 --> 01:14:53,479
[SPEAKER_08] kako, odnosno

1088
01:14:53,479 --> 01:14:55,420
[SPEAKER_08] davam li odgovor,

1089
01:14:55,420 --> 01:14:57,520
[SPEAKER_08] to je da budemo glasnici.

1090
01:14:57,520 --> 01:14:59,720
[SPEAKER_08] Glasnici toga

1091
01:14:59,720 --> 01:15:01,779
[SPEAKER_08] da potičemo recipročnost,

1092
01:15:01,779 --> 01:15:03,939
[SPEAKER_08] ono kako je rekao profesor Lujićino Bruni,

1093
01:15:03,939 --> 01:15:05,180
[SPEAKER_08] da budemo otvoreni,

1094
01:15:05,180 --> 01:15:06,859
[SPEAKER_08] da nam odnosi mogu

1095
01:15:06,859 --> 01:15:09,300
[SPEAKER_08] biti i rana i blagoslov.

1096
01:15:09,300 --> 01:15:12,020
[SPEAKER_08] Dakle, da ne smijemo nikako težiti

1097
01:15:12,020 --> 01:15:12,720
[SPEAKER_08] na toj,

1098
01:15:12,720 --> 01:15:15,239
[SPEAKER_08] kako je on rekao,

1099
01:15:15,239 --> 01:15:17,020
[SPEAKER_08] ugovornosti,

1100
01:15:17,020 --> 01:15:17,819
[SPEAKER_08] odnosno

1101
01:15:17,819 --> 01:15:19,579
[SPEAKER_08] ono imunosti

1102
01:15:19,579 --> 01:15:21,119
[SPEAKER_08] koja se stječe,

1103
01:15:21,119 --> 01:15:23,220
[SPEAKER_08] koja preko ugovornosti.

1104
01:15:23,220 --> 01:15:24,199
[SPEAKER_08] Tako da,

1105
01:15:24,199 --> 01:15:25,319
[SPEAKER_08] mislim da mi moramo biti

1106
01:15:25,319 --> 01:15:26,020
[SPEAKER_08] ti glasnici

1107
01:15:26,020 --> 01:15:26,659
[SPEAKER_08] svega onoga

1108
01:15:26,659 --> 01:15:27,859
[SPEAKER_08] novoga što donosi

1109
01:15:27,859 --> 01:15:28,819
[SPEAKER_08] Franjina ekonomija.

1110
01:15:28,819 --> 01:15:30,100
[SPEAKER_08] Puno toga novoga ima.

1111
01:15:30,100 --> 01:15:31,060
[SPEAKER_08] Dobro ga,

1112
01:15:31,060 --> 01:15:31,380
[SPEAKER_08] evo,

1113
01:15:31,380 --> 01:15:32,699
[SPEAKER_08] Ingrid je na početku rekla

1114
01:15:32,699 --> 01:15:33,800
[SPEAKER_08] ovaj način,

1115
01:15:33,800 --> 01:15:35,520
[SPEAKER_08] ovo poznavanje,

1116
01:15:35,520 --> 01:15:36,760
[SPEAKER_08] ulaženje u ekonominanje

1117
01:15:36,760 --> 01:15:37,939
[SPEAKER_08] dosta strano.

1118
01:15:37,939 --> 01:15:38,680
[SPEAKER_08] Namo u Hrvatskoj,

1119
01:15:38,680 --> 01:15:40,500
[SPEAKER_08] vjerojatno u veliko većini svijeta,

1120
01:15:40,500 --> 01:15:42,760
[SPEAKER_08] Italija tu nešto napreduje.

1121
01:15:42,760 --> 01:15:43,899
[SPEAKER_08] Mogu svjedeći samo,

1122
01:15:43,899 --> 01:15:45,000
[SPEAKER_08] prije par dana

1123
01:15:45,000 --> 01:15:45,819
[SPEAKER_08] se udjelovala sam

1124
01:15:45,819 --> 01:15:48,220
[SPEAKER_08] na jednom studijskom danu

1125
01:15:48,220 --> 01:15:50,500
[SPEAKER_08] za osobe posvećenog života

1126
01:15:50,500 --> 01:15:53,079
[SPEAKER_08] i teološki pogled na ekonomiju,

1127
01:15:53,079 --> 01:15:54,840
[SPEAKER_08] gdje je voditelj programa

1128
01:15:54,840 --> 01:15:55,939
[SPEAKER_08] bio profesor Bruni

1129
01:15:55,939 --> 01:15:57,300
[SPEAKER_08] i rekao je,

1130
01:15:57,300 --> 01:15:57,520
[SPEAKER_08] da,

1131
01:15:57,520 --> 01:15:57,739
[SPEAKER_08] evo,

1132
01:15:57,739 --> 01:15:59,500
[SPEAKER_08] ističem samo jednu crticu,

1133
01:15:59,500 --> 01:16:01,159
[SPEAKER_08] organizacije koje

1134
01:16:01,159 --> 01:16:02,079
[SPEAKER_08] u svojom,

1135
01:16:02,079 --> 01:16:04,579
[SPEAKER_08] u svojom težnjem svom radu

1136
01:16:04,579 --> 01:16:06,039
[SPEAKER_08] imaju u vidu,

1137
01:16:06,039 --> 01:16:06,340
[SPEAKER_08] odnosno,

1138
01:16:06,340 --> 01:16:08,560
[SPEAKER_08] hode k jednom idealizmu,

1139
01:16:08,560 --> 01:16:09,239
[SPEAKER_08] odnosno,

1140
01:16:09,319 --> 01:16:10,220
[SPEAKER_08] slijedi jedan ideal,

1141
01:16:10,220 --> 01:16:14,000
[SPEAKER_08] one se najčešće sastoje od 10% osoba

1142
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:15,500
[SPEAKER_08] koje su potpuno lojalne,

1143
01:16:15,500 --> 01:16:18,479
[SPEAKER_08] 10% osoba koje nisu lojalne

1144
01:16:18,479 --> 01:16:21,020
[SPEAKER_08] i 80% osoba su one osobe

1145
01:16:21,020 --> 01:16:22,399
[SPEAKER_08] koje imitiraju.

1146
01:16:22,399 --> 01:16:23,239
[SPEAKER_08] E sad,

1147
01:16:23,239 --> 01:16:27,279
[SPEAKER_08] normalno da je idealno bi bilo da imitiraju one koje su potpuno lojalne.

1148
01:16:27,720 --> 01:16:31,079
[SPEAKER_08] To vjerujem zahtjeva jedan veliki angažman,

1149
01:16:31,079 --> 01:16:32,199
[SPEAKER_08] pa ne znam,

1150
01:16:32,199 --> 01:16:34,060
[SPEAKER_08] meni to bi je takako jedan veliki poticaj

1151
01:16:34,060 --> 01:16:37,699
[SPEAKER_08] prepoznati se u ulozi glasnika.

1152
01:16:37,699 --> 01:16:39,479
[SPEAKER_08] To je isto dio franjene ekonomije,

1153
01:16:39,479 --> 01:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_08] odnosno karizma franjene ekonomije,

1154
01:16:41,000 --> 01:16:42,699
[SPEAKER_08] odnosno samog svetofranje,

1155
01:16:42,699 --> 01:16:45,039
[SPEAKER_08] da je bio glasnik velikog kralja,

1156
01:16:45,039 --> 01:16:47,399
